[[File:Joe_and_Jilly_Biden_early_photo.jpg|thumb]]，两人于1975年相识，1977年结婚]]
1973年1月5日，拜登在威尔明顿医疗中心特拉华分院儿子的病床旁宣誓就职，见证者為[[美国参议院|参议院]]秘书长弗朗西斯·瓦莱奥（Francis R. Valeo）。<ref name="ap-sworn">{{Cite news |date=1973-01-06 |title=Oath Solemn |page=11 |work=Spokane Daily Chronicle |agency=Associated Press |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=yadYAAAAIBAJ&pg=5556,1874966 |accessdate=2020-12-16 |archive-date=2021-01-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210103080828/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=yadYAAAAIBAJ&pg=5556%2C1874966 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="witcover" />{{rp|93, 98}}在场的人包括儿子[[博·拜登|博·拜登]]（他的腿还在车祸所致的牵引架中）等家庭成员。<ref name="ap-sworn" /><ref name="witcover" />{{rp|93, 98}}當時以拜登30岁之齡，成为了美国历史上第六年轻的参议员。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Youngest Senator |url=https://www.senate.gov/artandhistory/history/minute/Youngest_Senator.htm |access-date=2008-08-25 |publisher=United States Senate |archive-date=2002-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20021226155950/https://www.senate.gov/artandhistory/history/minute/Youngest_Senator.htm |dead-url=no }} {{PD-notice}}</ref><ref>Byrd, Robert and Wolff, Wendy ''[https://books.google.com/books?id=PeHByMYxVm8C&pg=PA285 Senate, 1789–1989: Historical Statistics, 1789–1992, Volume 4] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=PeHByMYxVm8C&pg=PA285 |date=20210103080837 }}'', p. 285 (Government Printing Office 1993) {{PD-notice}}</ref>

为了能每天见到他的儿子们<ref name="family values">{{Cite news |last=Pride |first=Mike |date=2007-12-01 |title=Biden a smart guy who has lived his family values |work=Concord Monitor |url=http://concordmonitor.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20071201/OPINION/712010307 |access-date=2008-10-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071203001952/http://concordmonitor.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20071201%2FOPINION%2F712010307 |archive-date=2007-12-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，拜登每天都需要从位于[[威尔明顿_(特拉华州)|威尔明顿]]的寓所搭乘一个半小时的[[美鐵|美鐵]]火车到[[华盛顿特区|华盛顿特区]]，这个习惯贯穿了他的参议院生涯，一连保持了36年。<ref name="aap08-bio" />而突如其来的劫难也让拜登一度十分怀疑宗教，他后来写道，他“觉得上帝对他玩了一个可怕的把戏”，<ref>Biden, ''Promises to Keep'', p. 81</ref>並使之有时难以集中在工作上。<ref name="nyt-ease">{{Cite news |last=Bumiller |first=Elisabeth |date=2007-12-14 |title=Biden Campaigning With Ease After Hardships |work=The New York Times |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2007/12/14/us/politics/14biden.html |access-date=2008-09-13 |archive-date=2008-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081210154755/http://www.nytimes.com/2007/12/14/us/politics/14biden.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="npr-int">{{Cite news |date=2007-08-01 |title=On Becoming Joe Biden |work=Morning Edition |publisher=NPR |url=https://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=12389154 |access-date=2008-09-12 |archive-date=2008-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080909093445/http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=12389154 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

拜登对第二任妻子[[吉尔·特蕾西·雅各布斯|吉尔·特蕾西·雅各布斯]]让他重拾了对政治和生活的兴趣。<ref>Biden, ''Promises to Keep'', p. 113.</ref>两人在1975年通过朋友介绍相识<ref name="nyt082508">{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2008/08/25/us/politics/25wife.html |title=Jill Biden Heads Toward Life in the Spotlight |last=Seelye |first=Katharine Q. |newspaper=The New York Times |date=2008-08-24 |accessdate=2008-08-25 |archive-date=2008-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081210193454/http://www.nytimes.com/2008/08/25/us/politics/25wife.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，後於1977年6月17日在纽约的[[联合国|联合国]]小教堂举行了婚礼<ref name="coxns-jill">{{cite news |url=https://www.orlandosentinel.com/news/os-xpm-2008-10-24-a3bidenwife24-story.html |title=Bidens met, forged life together after tragedy |last=Dart |first=Bob |agency=Cox News Service |newspaper=Orlando Sentinel |date=2008-10-24 |accessdate=2020-12-16 |archive-date=2020-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020153208/https://www.orlandosentinel.com/news/os-xpm-2008-10-24-a3bidenwife24-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>Biden, ''Promises to Keep'', p. 117.</ref>两人都是[[天主教|天主教]]徒，在特拉华州[[格林維爾_(特拉華州)|格林維爾布兰迪河]]畔的圣约瑟夫教堂参加弥撒。<ref>{{cite news |title=Parishioners not surprised to see Biden at usual Mass |last=Gibson |first=Ginger |newspaper=The News Journal |date=2008-08-25 |page=A.12 |url=https://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/delawareonline/access/1742751081.html?FMT=ABS |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130601093036/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/delawareonline/access/1742751081.html?FMT=ABS |archivedate=2013-06-01 |accessdate=2020-12-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>他们的女儿[[阿什莉·拜登|阿什莉·拜登]]生于1981年<ref name="ap-timeline" />，成为了一位社会工作者。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/06/03/fashion/weddings/ashley-biden-howard-krein-wedding.html |title=Ashley Biden and Howard Krein |newspaper=The New York Times |date=2012-06-03 |page=ST15 |accessdate=2020-12-16 |archive-date=2020-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101001405/https://www.nytimes.com/2012/06/03/fashion/weddings/ashley-biden-howard-krein-wedding.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>亨特·拜登成为了在[[华盛顿哥伦比亚特区|华盛顿]]的律师和[[游说集团|游说家]]。<ref name="nydn122808">{{cite news |url=http://www.nydailynews.com/news/politics/2008/12/27/2008-12-27_from_a_blind_date_to_second_lady_jill_bi.html |title=From a blind date to second lady, Jill Biden's coming into her own |last=Evans |first=Heidi |newspaper=Daily News |location=New York |date=2008-12-28 |accessdate=2009-01-03 |archive-date=2009-01-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090104002628/http://www.nydailynews.com/news/politics/2008/12/27/2008-12-27_from_a_blind_date_to_second_lady_jill_bi.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>拜登的长子[[博·拜登|博·拜登]]是一名相貌堂堂的青年才俊，长大后步父亲后尘进入法律界及政界，成为了特拉华州的总检察长<ref>{{cite news|accessdate=2008-08-23|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB121919956426355701|title=Biden's Foreign Policy Background Carries Growing Cachet|last=Cooper|first=Christopher|newspaper=The Wall Street Journal|date=2008-08-20|page=A4|archive-date=2013-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130813071718/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB121919956426355701.html?mod=googlenews_wsj|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并曾参军赴[[伊拉克|伊拉克]]驻扎，在成為少校後退役。然而天妒英才，博·拜登由于罹患脑癌不治，于2015年5月30日不幸病逝，年仅46岁。<ref name="nydn122808" />这使得經歷本就坎坷的拜登老年丧子，悲痛不已。

从1991年至2008年，拜登在{{Link-en|威德恩大学法学院|Widener University Delaware Law School}}与其他教授一起执教了一门[[宪法学|宪法学]][[研討會|研討會]]，<ref name="#1">{{Cite web|title=Who is Tony Bobulinski, Hunter Biden's former business associate?|url=https://www.foxnews.com/politics/who-is-tony-bobulinski-hunter-bidens-former-business-associate|accessdate=2020-12-14|date=2020-10-22|last=Barrabi|first=Thomas|work=Fox News|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106195410/https://www.foxnews.com/politics/who-is-tony-bobulinski-hunter-bidens-former-business-associate|dead-url=no}}</ref>该研讨会在学生中非常火爆，供不应求，课的空位时常有个等候名单。拜登有时候还会从海外专门飞回特拉华州教课。<ref>{{cite web|title=Faculty: Joseph R. Biden, Jr.|url=http://law.widener.edu/Academics/Faculty/ProfilesDeAdj/BidenJosephR.aspx|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081006123224/http://law.widener.edu/Academics/Faculty/ProfilesDeAdj/BidenJosephR.aspx|archive-date=2008-10-06|accessdate=2008-09-24|publisher=Widener University School of Law|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="wid-veep-elect" /><ref>{{cite news|last=Purchla|first=Matt|date=2008-08-26|title=For Widener Law students, a teacher aims high|publisher=Metro Philadelphia|url=http://philly.metro.us/metro/local/article/For_Widener_Law_students_a_teacher_aims_high/13457.html|accessdate=2008-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081004214751/http://philly.metro.us/metro/local/article/For_Widener_Law_students_a_teacher_aims_high/13457.html|archive-date=2008-10-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Carey|first=Kathleen E.|date=2008-08-27|title=Widener students proud of Biden|publisher=Delaware County Daily and Sunday Times|url=http://www.delcotimes.com/site/news.cfm?newsid=20094884&BRD=1675&PAG=461&dept_id=18171&rfi=6|accessdate=2008-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080919152356/http://www.delcotimes.com/site/news.cfm?newsid=20094884&BRD=1675&PAG=461&dept_id=18171&rfi=6|archive-date=2008-09-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>

