拜登從事参议员不久，便专注于[[消费者保护|消费者保护]]和[[环境问题|环境问题]]，他还呼吁加强政府[[問責制|問責制]]。<ref name="time-200-fut">{{Cite news |date=1974-07-15 |title=200 Faces for the Future |work=[[Time_(magazine)|Time]] |url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,879402-6,00.html |access-date=2008-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130813045404/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,879402-6,00.html |archive-date=2013-08-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>在1974年的一次采访中，他称自己在公民权利和自由、老年人关注的问题和医疗保健方面是自由派，但在其他问题上，包括[[堕胎|堕胎]]和[[征兵|征兵]]问题上则偏向保守派。<ref name="The Washingtonian-June-1974">{{Cite news |last=Kelley |first=Kitty |date=1974-06-01 |title=Death and the All-American Boy |work=The Washingtonian |url=https://www.washingtonian.com/1974/06/01/joe-biden-kitty-kelley-1974-profile-death-and-the-all-american-boy/ |access-date=2020-03-08 |archive-date=2020-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201110162757/https://www.washingtonian.com/1974/06/01/joe-biden-kitty-kelley-1974-profile-death-and-the-all-american-boy/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

拜登在任期前十年关注于[[軍控|軍控]]问题。<ref name="nyt-foreign" /><ref name="cby-45">''Current Biography Yearbook 1987'', p. 45.</ref>在国会未能批准苏联[[苏联共产党中央委员会总书记|总书记]][[列昂尼德·伊里奇·勃列日涅夫|列昂尼德·伊里奇·勃列日涅夫]]和[[吉米·卡特|吉米·卡特]]总统于1979年签署的《[[战略武器限制谈判|美苏限制进攻性战略武器条约（SALT II）]]》后，拜登会见了[[苏联外交部|苏联外交部]]长[[安德烈·葛罗米柯|安德烈·葛罗米柯]]，传达了美国的关切，并争取到了针对美国参议院外交关系委员会所提之反对意见的调整。<ref>{{Cite book|last=Salacuse|first=Jeswald W.|url=https://archive.org/details/leadingleaders00jesw|title=Leading Leaders: How to Manage Smart, Talented, Rich and Powerful People|publisher=American Management Association|year=2005|isbn=0-8144-0855-9}} p. 144.</ref>在里根政府想故意对1972年所签的《[[战略武器限制谈判|美苏关于限制进攻性战略武器的某些措施的临时协定]]》以宽泛的方式解释，以允许制定《[[星球大战计划|星球大战计划]]》时，拜登则主张严格遵守该条约。<ref name="nyt-foreign" />拜登还在参议院听证会上斥责国务卿[[乔治·普拉特·舒尔茨|乔治·舒尔茨]]，指责里根政府不顾南非的[[种族隔离|种族隔离]]政策继续支持南非，受到了广泛关注。<ref name="dmn-87" />

1981年，拜登成为了参议院司法委员会的成员。1984年，他曾代表民主党负责并成功通过了《{{Link-en|1984年综合犯罪控制法案|Comprehensive Crime Control Act of 1984}}》。随着时间的推移，该法对犯罪行为的严苛刑罚引起了争议。2019年，拜登承认自己推动该法案，是「犯下了大錯」。<ref>{{Cite news |last=Herndon |first=Astead W. |date=2019-01-21 |title=Biden Expresses Regret for Support of Crime Legislation in the 1990s |work=The New York Times |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2019/01/21/us/politics/biden-crime-bill-regrets.html |access-date=2019-01-21 |issn=0362-4331 |archive-date=2020-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201110162903/https://www.nytimes.com/2019/01/21/us/politics/biden-crime-bill-regrets.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[https://www.nytimes.com/2019/01/06/us/politics/joe-biden-2020-president.html "Biden in 2020? Allies Say He Sees Himself as Democrats' Best Hope"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2019/01/06/us/politics/joe-biden-2020-president.html |date=20201110163104 }}, By Jonathan Martin and Alexander Burns. ''New York Times''. January 6, 2019</ref>拜登的支持者称赞他修改了该法案中最糟糕的条款，这是他在该时期立法方面取得的最重大的成就。<ref name="cby-44" />该法案包括了《{{Link-en|联邦攻击性武器禁令|Federal Assault Weapons Ban}}》<ref>{{cite news|last=Fifield|first=Anna|date=2013-01-04|title=Biden faces key role in second term|newspaper=[[Financial_Times|Financial Times]]|url=https://www.ft.com/content/412f47b0-5694-11e2-aad0-00144feab49a|accessdate=2020-12-17|archive-date=2021-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210103081008/https://www.ft.com/content/412f47b0-5694-11e2-aad0-00144feab49a|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="time-cov-0113" />和《{{Link-en|针对妇女的暴力行为法|Violence Against Women Act}}》。<ref>{{cite web|title=Domestic Violence|url=http://biden.senate.gov/issues/issue/?id=975b0cf4-ce25-42cc-b63d-072fb81e8618|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080822144642/http://biden.senate.gov/issues/issue/?id=975b0cf4-ce25-42cc-b63d-072fb81e8618|archive-date=2008-08-22|accessdate=2008-09-09|publisher=Biden Senate Website|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1993年，拜登对一项认为[[同性戀|同性戀]]与军旅生活不相容的条款投了赞成票，从而禁止了同性恋者服役。<ref>{{Cite web |title=govinfo |url=https://www.govinfo.gov/app/details/USCODE-2010-title10/USCODE-2010-title10-subtitleA-partII-chap37-sec654 |access-date=2019-05-06 |website=govinfo.gov |archive-date=2019-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190506191328/https://www.govinfo.gov/app/details/USCODE-2010-title10/USCODE-2010-title10-subtitleA-partII-chap37-sec654 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |last1=Epstein |first1=Reid J. |last2=Lerer |first2=Lisa |date=2019-09-20 |title=Joe Biden Has Tense Exchange Over L.G.B.T.Q. Record |work=The New York Times |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2019/09/20/us/politics/lgbt-forum-2020.html |access-date=2020-04-15 |issn=0362-4331 |archive-date=2020-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200416100800/https://www.nytimes.com/2019/09/20/us/politics/lgbt-forum-2020.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |last=A. Del |first=Jose |title=Sanders attacks Biden's record on gay rights and women's issues |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/sanders-calls-biden-my-friend-then-he-goes-on-the-attack/2020/03/08/20a23f86-60d0-11ea-9055-5fa12981bbbf_story.html |access-date=2020-04-15 |website=Washington Post |archive-date=2020-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200308233903/https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/sanders-calls-biden-my-friend-then-he-goes-on-the-attack/2020/03/08/20a23f86-60d0-11ea-9055-5fa12981bbbf_story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>1996年，他投票赞成《[[捍卫婚姻法案|捍卫婚姻法案]]》，该法案禁止联邦政府承认[[同性婚姻|同性婚姻]]，从而禁止这类婚姻中的个人获得联邦法律的平等保护，并允许各州也这样做。<ref>{{Cite web |title=U.S. Senate: U.S. Senate Roll Call Votes 104th Congress—2nd Session |url=https://www.senate.gov/legislative/LIS/roll_call_lists/roll_call_vote_cfm.cfm?congress=104&session=2&vote=00280 |access-date=2019-06-12 |website=senate.gov |archive-date=2005-05-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050507161358/http://www.senate.gov/legislative/LIS/roll_call_lists/roll_call_vote_cfm.cfm?congress=104 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2015年，该法案在[[奥贝格费尔诉霍奇斯案|奥贝格费尔诉霍奇斯案]]中被裁定违宪。<ref>{{Cite web |last1=de Vogue |first1=Ariane |last2=Diamond |first2=Jeremy |title=Supreme Court rules states must allow same-sex marriage |url=https://www.cnn.com/2015/06/26/politics/supreme-court-same-sex-marriage-ruling/index.html |access-date=2019-06-12 |website=CNN |archive-date=2015-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150627065146/https://www.cnn.com/2015/06/26/politics/supreme-court-same-sex-marriage-ruling/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 反对种族融合校车 ===

拜登在70年代中期是参议院{{Link-en|种族融合校车|Desegregation busing}}政策的主要反对者之一。主要原因是他的特拉华州选民强烈反对，这种全国范围内的反对意见导致民主党放弃了多数针对学校的种族融合政策。<ref name="Gadsen">{{Cite news |last=Gadsden |first=Brett |date=2019-05-05 |title=Here's How Deep Biden's Busing Problem Runs |work=Politico |url=https://www.politico.com/magazine/story/2019/05/05/joe-biden-busing-problem-226791 |access-date=2019-05-05 |archive-date=2019-05-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190505123922/https://www.politico.com/magazine/story/2019/05/05/joe-biden-busing-problem-226791 |dead-url=no }}</ref>在第一次参议院竞选中，拜登曾表示支持用校车来补救[[De_jure|法律上的]][[吉姆·克勞法|隔离政策]]，如[[美國南部|美國南方]][[吉姆·克勞法|所作所为]]，但反对用校车来补救因不同种族在某个地区居住而导致的[[De_facto|实际上]]的隔离。在特拉华州，拜登则反对了一条拟议将会完全禁止校车的宪法修正案。{{sfn|Gadsen|2012|page=214}}

1974年5月，拜登投票决定搁置一项包含反滥用和反隔离条款的提案，但后来又投票支持一个修改后的版本，其中包含一个限定条件，即该提案无意削弱司法部门执行[[美國憲法第五修正案|憲法第五修正案]]和[[美利坚合众国宪法第十四条修正案|第十四修正案]]的权力。<ref name="Sokol">{{Cite news |last=Sokol |first=Jason |date=2019-04-25 |title=How a Young Joe Biden Turned Liberals Against Integration |work=Politico |url=https://www.politico.com/magazine/story/2015/08/04/joe-biden-integration-school-busing-120968 |access-date=2019-04-25 |archive-date=2020-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201110162959/https://www.politico.com/magazine/story/2015/08/04/joe-biden-integration-school-busing-120968 |dead-url=no }}</ref>1975年，他支持一项将阻止卫生、教育和福利部削减联邦资金给拒绝融合的地区的提案。{{sfn|Gadsen|2012|pages=220–221}}拜登称：“种族融合校车的想法（违反）基本的常识”，而他的反对让自由主义者更容易效仿类似立场。<ref name="cby-44">''Current Biography Yearbook 1987'', p. 44.</ref>同时拜登支持关于[[住房权|住房]]、[[就業機會|就業機會]]和[[投票權|投票權]]的倡议。拜登支持了一项法案，规定只允许使用联邦资金将学生送到离住地最近的学校。1977年，拜登与他人共同提出了一项修正案，以弥补该措施的漏洞，[[吉米·卡特|卡特]]总统于1978年将其签署为法律。<ref name="Raffel1998">{{Cite book |last=Raffel |first=Jeffrey A. |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=gA1JljCpxzEC&pg=PA90 |title=Historical Dictionary of School Segregation and Desegregation: The American Experience |publisher=Greenwood Publishing Group |year=1998 |isbn=978-0-313-29502-7 |page=90 |access-date=2020-12-17 |archive-date=2020-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930184823/https://books.google.com/books?id=gA1JljCpxzEC&pg=PA90 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 1988年参选总统 ===
