b|title=Is new PAC Joe Biden's last act in politics or first step toward 2020?|url=https://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/democrats-vs-trump/new-pac-joe-biden-s-last-act-politics-or-first-n766891|accessdate=2020-12-14|work=NBC News|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210103083117/https://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/democrats-vs-trump/new-pac-joe-biden-s-last-act-politics-or-first-n766891|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://americanpossibilities.org/ |title=「美國可能性」（American Possibilities）官方網站 |access-date=2017-06-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170608224707/https://americanpossibilities.org/ |archive-date=2017-06-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

2018年，拜登为有所交情的[[亚利桑那州|亚利桑那州]]已故参议员[[约翰·麦凯恩|约翰·麦凯恩]]致悼词，称赞他对美国精神的维护和跨越党派的友谊。拜登仍留在公众视野中为候选人背书，同时继续对政治、[[氣候變遷|氣候變遷]]和時任总统[[唐納·川普|特朗普]]等議題发表评论。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.politico.com/states/new-jersey/story/2017/05/28/biden-backing-phil-murphy-says-nj-governors-race-single-most-important-112380|title=Biden backs Phil Murphy, says N.J. governor's race 'most important' in nation|first=Ryan|last=Hutchins|date=2017-05-28|publisher=Politico|accessdate=2020-12-14|archive-date=2019-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191230125059/https://www.politico.com/states/new-jersey/story/2017/05/28/biden-backing-phil-murphy-says-nj-governors-race-single-most-important-112380|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=The Democratic candidates on foreign policy |url=https://foreignpolicy.com/2020-election/ |work=[[Foreign_Policy|Foreign Policy]] |accessdate=2020-12-14 |archive-date=2020-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200616084737/https://foreignpolicy.com/2020-election/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://thehill.com/policy/energy-environment/335859-biden-paris-deal-best-way-to-protect-us-leadership|title=Biden: Paris deal 'best way to protect' US leadership|first=Max|last=Greenwood|newspaper=The Hill|date=2017-05-31|accessdate=2020-12-14|archive-date=2020-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200225090215/https://thehill.com/policy/energy-environment/335859-biden-paris-deal-best-way-to-protect-us-leadership|dead-url=no}}</ref>他还继续为[[LGBT权利|LGBT权利]]发声，倡导这个在其副总统任内与他关系更为密切的议题。<ref>{{cite news |title=VP's LGBT comments raise eyebrows |url=https://www.politico.com/story/2014/03/joe-biden-lgbt-workplace-discrimination-executive-order-human-rights-campaign-105018 |work=Politico.com |accessdate=2020-12-14 |archive-date=2021-01-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210103083142/https://www.politico.com/story/2014/03/joe-biden-lgbt-workplace-discrimination-executive-order-human-rights-campaign-105018 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.seattletimes.com/nation-world/joe-biden-to-lgbt-gala-hold-president-trump-accountable/|title=Joe Biden to LGBT gala: 'Hold President Trump accountable'|date=2017-06-21|first=Steve|last=Peoples|newspaper=Seattle Times|accessdate=2020-12-14|archive-date=2020-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200620090144/https://www.seattletimes.com/nation-world/joe-biden-to-lgbt-gala-hold-president-trump-accountable//|dead-url=no}}</ref>2019年，拜登批评[[文莱|文莱]]打算实施[[伊斯兰教法|伊斯兰法律]]，允许对[[通奸|通奸]]和[[同性恋|同性恋]]者处以[[石刑|石刑]]。拜登称这是“骇人听闻和不道德的”，并说：“不能用文化和传统為这种仇恨和不人道的行为開脫。”<ref>{{Cite news|title=Brunei defends tough new Islamic laws against growing backlash|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-brunei-islamiclaws-idUSKCN1RB0E1|newspaper=Reuters|date=2019-03-30|accessdate=2020-12-14|language=en|first=Reuters|last=Staff|archive-date=2020-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200620090148/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-brunei-islamiclaws-idUSKCN1RB0E1/|dead-url=no}}</ref>拜登和他的妻子报告说，截至2019年，因为演讲活动和写书的合同，他们的资产增加到了220万美元到800万美元之间。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Eder|first1=Steve|last2=Glueck|first2=Katie|date=2019-07-09|title=Joe Biden's Tax Returns Show More Than $15 Million in Income After 2016|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2019/07/09/us/politics/joe-biden-net-worth.html|accessdate=2019-07-16|archive-date=2019-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190715211457/https://www.nytimes.com/2019/07/09/us/politics/joe-biden-net-worth.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

