Chinese firm |work=Daily Mail Online |date=2020-10-22 |accessdate=2020-10-22 |archive-date=2021-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210201022707/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-8866713/Hunter-Bidens-ex-business-partner-says-Joe-Biden-talked-son-deal-Chinese-firm.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>鮑布林斯基随后在接受福斯新聞頻道采访时表示，乔·拜登涉嫌与一家中国能源公司的合资公司有联系。<ref>{{Cite web|title='Plausible deniability': Tony Bobulinski claims Biden family shrugged off concerns about risk to 2020 bid|url=https://www.foxnews.com/politics/plausible-deniability-tony-bobulinski-biden-family|accessdate=2020-12-14|date=2020-10-27|last=Shaw|first=Adam|work=Fox News|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210203194008/https://www.foxnews.com/politics/plausible-deniability-tony-bobulinski-biden-family|dead-url=no}}</ref>但是，《[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]》所获的的公司记录显示，乔·拜登与鮑布林斯基所指的合资公司没有任何关联。该合资公司，在2017年拜登卸任副总统后成立，从未收到中国公司的拟议投资或完成了任何交易。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Hunter Biden’s Ex-Business Partner Alleges Father Knew About Venture|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/hunter-bidens-ex-business-partner-alleges-father-knew-about-venture-11603421247|newspaper=Wall Street Journal|date=2020-10-23|accessdate=2020-12-14|issn=0099-9660|language=en-US|first=Andrew Duehren and James T.|last=Areddy|archive-date=2021-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210203205255/https://www.wsj.com/articles/hunter-bidens-ex-business-partner-alleges-father-knew-about-venture-11603421247|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 成功当选 ===
{{further|乔·拜登的总统过渡}}
2020年11月，新一届[[2020年美國總統選舉|美國總統選舉]]如期举行。根据各州投票结果，拜登以306:232的巨大优势击败了前任总统[[唐纳德·特朗普|唐纳德·特朗普]]及副总统[[迈克·彭斯|迈克·彭斯]]，当选为美国第46任总统，其搭档副总统为[[贺锦丽|贺锦丽]]。自此，拜登成为自1992年[[比尔·克林顿|比尔·克林顿]]击败乔治·布什以来第一位击败现任总统的候选人。<ref name="Azari">{{Cite news |last=Azari |first=Julia |date=2020-08-20 |title=Biden Had To Fight For The Presidential Nomination. But Most VPs Have To. |work=FiveThirtyEight |url=https://fivethirtyeight.com/features/biden-had-to-fight-for-the-presidential-nomination-but-most-vps-have-to/ |access-date=2020-08-25 |archive-date=2020-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201117190453/https://fivethirtyeight.com/features/biden-had-to-fight-for-the-presidential-nomination-but-most-vps-have-to/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>他是第二位非现任副总统（继1968年的理查德·尼克松之后）当选总统，也有望成为最年长的总统，<ref>{{Cite web|last=Peter|first=Josh|date=2020-11-05|title=Joe Biden will become the oldest president in American history, a title previously held by Ronald Reagan|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2020/11/05/oldest-president-joe-biden/6181672002/|access-date=2020-11-18|website=USA Today|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107182039/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2020/11/05/oldest-president-joe-biden/6181672002/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-11-20|title=Birthday time: Biden turns 78, will be oldest U.S. president|url=https://apnews.com/article/joe-biden-donald-trump-health-ronald-reagan-coronavirus-pandemic-b43ea0d0049ae2cd72aead6e1816f6d5|access-date=2020-12-09|website=AP NEWS|archive-date=2020-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201209011436/https://apnews.com/article/joe-biden-donald-trump-health-ronald-reagan-coronavirus-pandemic-b43ea0d0049ae2cd72aead6e1816f6d5|dead-url=no}}</ref>同时也是第一位家乡是[[特拉华州|特拉华州]]的总统（尽管他出生在[[宾夕法尼亚州|宾夕法尼亚州]]），以及继约翰·肯尼迪之后的第二位[[天主教|天主教]]总统。{{refn|name=GSA01b|group=注|然而，与之前的潜在过渡团队一样，如2012年落选候选人[[米特·罗姆尼|米特·罗姆尼]]的过渡团队，拜登的过渡团队仍无法根据2010年总统选举过渡法获得政府资助。<ref name="parker">{{cite news|last1=Parker|first1=Ashley|title=Campaigning Aside, Team Plans a Romney Presidency|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/08/17/us/politics/mitt-romneys-transition-team-is-hard-at-work.html?_r=0|accessdate=2016-01-22|newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=2012-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180205184839/http://www.nytimes.com/2012/08/17/us/politics/mitt-romneys-transition-team-is-hard-at-work.html?_r=0|archive-date=2018-02-05|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="nr">{{cite news|last1=Fund|first1=John|title=What was Romney Planning?|url=http://www.nationalreview.com/article/338182/what-was-romney-planning-john-fund|accessdate=2016-01-22|work=National Review|date=2013-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160131073601/http://www.nationalreview.com/article/338182/what-was-romney-planning-john-fund|archive-date=2016-01-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>但拜登自8月被提名以来，一直有资格接受机密情报简报。<ref name=CBS2020-09-18-01a>{{cite news|url=https://www.cbsnews.com/news/biden-receives-first-classified-intelligence-briefing/|work=CBS News|title=Biden receives first classified intelligence briefing|date=2020-09-18|first1=Olivia|last1=Gazis|first2=Bo|last2=Erickson|first3=Grace|last3=Segers|access-date=2020-10-22|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101043140/https://www.cbsnews.com/news/biden-receives-first-classified-intelligence-briefing/|dead-url=no}}</ref>据报道，截至2020年11月9日，至少有一些政府机构已经开始了他们的过渡计划，他家上空的空域受到限制，“特勤局已经开始使用其总统保护细节中的特工为当选总统及其家人服务。”<ref name=TribuneIndia2020-11-09-01a>{{cite news|url=https://www.tribuneindia.com/news/health/trump-faces-calls-to-work-with-biden-team-on-transition-168288|newspaper=The Tribune|title=Trump faces calls to work with Biden team on transition|date=2020-11-09|accessdate=2020-11-09|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115190525/https://www.tribuneindia.com/news/health/trump-faces-calls-to-work-with-biden-team-on-transition-168288|dead-url=no}}</ref>}}

大选后几天，拜登成立了[[COVID-19|COVID-19]]咨询委员会，以取代之前的白宫冠状病毒特别工作组。<ref>{{Cite web|last=Feuer|first=Will|date=2020-11-07|title=President-elect Joe Biden to announce Covid task force on Monday|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2020/11/07/president-elect-joe-biden-to-announce-covid-task-force-on-monday.html|access-date=2020-11-08|publisher=CNBC|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107212640/https://www.cnbc.com/2020/11/07/president-elect-joe-biden-to-announce-covid-task-force-on-monday.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|last1=Mercia|first1=Dan|last2=Zeleny|first2=Jeff|date=2020-11-07|title=Biden to announce coronavirus task force as part of presidential transition|publisher=[[CNN|CNN]]|url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/11/07/politics/transition-biden-coronavirus-task-force/index.html|access-date=2020-11-09|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108213501/https://www.cnn.com/2020/11/07/politics/transition-biden-coronavirus-task-force/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>他承诺，政府将采取比特朗普更有力的应对措施，<ref name="GoodStol">{{cite news |last1=Goodnough |first1=Abby |last2=Stolberg |first2=Sheryl Gay |title=Biden's Covid Response Plan Draws From F.D.R.'s New Deal |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/10/14/health/covid-biden-pandemic-plan.html |accessdate=2020-11-07 |work=The New York Times |date=2020-10-15 |archive-date=2020-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201105212743/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/10/14/health/covid-biden-pandemic-plan.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>包括增加检测、稳定供应个人防护装备、分发疫苗，以及为学校和医院提供资金，所有这些都将由一个全国性的“供应链指挥”负责，他将协调[[个人防护装备|个人防护装备]]和检测包的制造和分发。测试材料将由“大流行病测试委员会”分发。<ref name="GoodStol" />拜登还承诺将比特朗普更积极地使用《[[国防生产法|国防生产法]]》来积累物资，并将雇佣10万名[[接触者追踪|接触者追踪者]]来追踪和限制疫情爆发。<ref name="GoodStol" />

2020年11月11日，拜登选择[[罗恩·克莱恩|罗恩·克莱恩]]为[[白宮幕僚長|白宮幕僚長]]。克莱恩在1980年代曾是拜登的参议院助手，是拜登作为副总统的第一任幕僚长，也是副总统[[阿尔·戈尔|阿尔·戈尔]]的幕僚长。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.politico.com/news/2020/11/11/biden-klain-chief-staff-436168 |title=Biden announces Ron Klain will be White House chief of staff |work=Politico |authors=Megan Cassella and Alex Thompson |date=2020-11-11 |accessdate=2020-11-12 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112030234/https://www.politico.com/news/2020/11/11/biden-klain-chief-staff-436168 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2020年11月23日，拜登首次作出国家安全提名和任命，提名[[安东尼·布林肯|安东尼·布林肯]]为国务卿，[[亚历杭德罗·马约尔卡斯|亚历杭德罗·马约尔卡斯]]为[[国土安全部|国土安全部]]部长，[[艾薇儿·海恩斯|艾薇儿·海恩斯]]为[[国家情报总监|国家情报总监]]，[[杰克·苏利文|杰克·苏利文]]为[[总统国家安全事务助理|总统国家安全事务助理]]，[[琳达·托马斯-格林菲尔德|琳达·托马斯-格林菲尔德]]为[[美国驻联合国大使|美国驻联合国大使]]，前国务卿[[約翰·福布斯·凱瑞|约翰·克里]]为总统气候问题特使。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://buildbackbetter.gov/the-administration/nominees-and-appointees/|title=Nominees and Appointees|publisher=Joe Biden presidential transition|access-date=2020-11-24|archive-date=2020-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124031258/https://buildbackbetter.gov/the-administration/nominees-and-appointees/|dead-url=no}}</ref>如果提名得到确认，海因斯将成为第一位担任国家情报总监的女性，马约卡斯将成为第一位担任美国国土安全部负责人的拉美人和第一位移民。拜登后来宣布，[[珍妮特·耶伦|珍妮特·耶伦]]是他提名的[[美国财政部长|财政部长]]人选。<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-12-16|title=All of President-elect Joe Biden’s Cabinet Nominees|url=https://nymag.com/intelligencer/article/joe-bidens-cabinet-begins-to-take-shape.html|access-date=2020-12-17|website=Intelligencer|archive-date=2020-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201215201511/https://nymag.com/intelligencer/article/joe-bidens-cabinet-begins-to-take-shape.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

同在11月23日，[[联邦总务署|联邦总务署]]署长艾米丽·墨菲正式承认拜登是2020年大选的赢家，并授权启动向拜登政府的过渡进程。<ref>{{cite news|work=[[CNN|CNN]]|url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/11/23/politics/transition-biden-gsa-begin/index.html|title=First on CNN: GSA tells Biden that transition can formally begin|authors=Kristen Holmes and Jeremy Herb|date=2020-11-23|access-date=2020-11-23|archive-date=2020-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123232709/https://www.cnn.com/2020/11/23/politics/transition-biden-gsa-begin/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>2020年12月21日，拜登在电视直播中接种了他的第一剂[[2019冠狀病毒病疫苗|2019冠狀病毒病疫苗]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://sd.iqilu.com/articlePc/detail/7356180.html|title=拜登公开接种新冠疫苗|archive-url=http://www.freezepage.com/1608596130YKFEIOGLJH|archive-date=2020-12-22|publisher=闪电新闻|accessdate=2020-12-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>，第二剂在2021年1月11日完成。<ref>{{Cite web|title=President-elect Biden receives final COVID-19 vaccine dose|url=https://www.wiproud.com/news/washington-dc/president-elect-biden-to-get-final-covid-19-vaccine-dose/|accessdate=2021-01-20|date=2021-01-11|work=FOX2548 & WIProud|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115080842/https://www.wiproud.com/news/washington-dc/president-elect-biden-to-get-final-covid-19-vaccine-dose/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2021年1月6日，美国国会最终清点了拜登与贺锦丽的选举人票数，正式确认了他们的正、副总统当选资格。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Joint Session of Congress Certifies Joe Biden as Next U.S. President|url=https://www.c-span.org/video/?507663-1/joint-session-congress-certifies-joe-biden-us-president|accessdate=2021-01-07|author=C-SPAN|date=2021-01-06|format=|publisher=C-SPAN|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107091551/https://www.c-span.org/video/?507663-1%2Fjoint-session-congress-certifies-joe-biden-us-president|dead-url=no}}</ref>

