2021年1月20日，拜登正式就任美国第46任总统。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Biden inauguration: New president sworn in amid Trump snub|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-55736856|newspaper=BBC News|date=2021-01-20|accessdate=2021-01-20|language=en-GB|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120145011/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-55736856|dead-url=no}}</ref>就职后，拜登成为了继[[约翰·肯尼迪|约翰·肯尼迪]]之后的第二位信奉[[天主教|天主教]]的总统<ref>{{Cite web|title=Joe Biden is the 2nd Catholic president in US history after JFK|url=https://www.today.com/news/joe-biden-2nd-catholic-president-us-history-after-jfk-t206253|accessdate=2021-01-20|work=TODAY.com|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128064812/https://www.today.com/news/joe-biden-2nd-catholic-president-us-history-after-jfk-t206253|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="delawareonlineinauguration" />，第一位[[特拉华州|特拉华州]]出身的总统，<ref name="delawareonlineinauguration">{{Cite web|title=President Biden: Longtime Delaware leader now takes the nation’s helm|url=https://www.delawareonline.com/story/news/politics/joe-biden/2021/01/20/joe-biden-oath-president-inauguration/4178642001/|accessdate=2021-01-20|last=Newman|first=Meredith|work=The News Journal|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129022052/https://www.delawareonline.com/story/news/politics/joe-biden/2021/01/20/joe-biden-oath-president-inauguration/4178642001/|dead-url=no}}</ref>并以78岁高龄成为了美国历史上最年长的总统。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Taking helm of divided nation, U.S. President Biden calls for end to 'uncivil war'|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/usa-biden-inauguration-int-idUSKBN29P0KH|newspaper=Reuters|date=2021-01-20|accessdate=2021-01-20|language=en|first=Trevor Hunnicutt, Patricia Zengerle, Jarrett|last=Renshaw|archive-date=2021-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210201193942/https://www.reuters.com/article/usa-biden-inauguration-int-idUSKBN29P0KH|dead-url=no}}</ref>前任总统[[唐纳德·特朗普|唐纳德·特朗普]]拒绝参加拜登的就职典礼，这是自[[理查德·尼克松|理查德·尼克松]]以来首次出现在世的任满或因故离任的前任总统缺席继任就职仪式。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Trump will be first president since Nixon to miss successor's inauguration|url=https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2021/jan/20/trump-biden-inauguration-richard-nixon|newspaper=The Guardian|date=2021-01-20|accessdate=2021-01-20|issn=0261-3077|language=en-GB|first=Rashida|last=Kamal|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126084337/https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2021/jan/20/trump-biden-inauguration-richard-nixon|dead-url=no}}</ref>前任副总统[[迈克·彭斯|彭斯]]伉儷出席了仪式。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Trump's vice president Pence applauds successor at inauguration|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-biden-inauguration-pence-idUSKBN29P2FV|newspaper=Reuters|date=2021-01-20|accessdate=2021-01-20|language=en|first=Andrea|last=Shalal|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124023824/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-biden-inauguration-pence-idUSKBN29P2FV|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 首100日 ===

上任首天，拜登就簽署了17項行政命令，涉及美國重返[[巴黎气候协议|巴黎气候协议]]、强制在[[联邦政府|联邦政府]]机构和联邦土地上佩戴口罩、撤销[[拱心石輸油管道|拱心石輸油管道]]第四期項目（Keystone XL）许可、结束了特朗普对数个[[穆斯林国家|穆斯林国家]]的旅行禁令、撤销特朗普下達的美国退出[[世界卫生组织|世界卫生组织]]命令、撤銷修建[[美墨边境墙|美墨边境墙]]等措施。<ref>{{cite news |title=新官上任三把火 拜登速发多项行政命令 |url=https://www.dw.com/zh/%E6%96%B0%E5%AE%98%E4%B8%8A%E4%BB%BB%E4%B8%89%E6%8A%8A%E7%81%AB-%E6%8B%9C%E7%99%BB%E9%80%9F%E5%8F%91%E5%A4%9A%E9%A1%B9%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/a-56296981 |accessdate=2021-01-21 |archive-date=2021-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210130122557/https://www.dw.com/zh/%E6%96%B0%E5%AE%98%E4%B8%8A%E4%BB%BB%E4%B8%89%E6%8A%8A%E7%81%AB-%E6%8B%9C%E7%99%BB%E9%80%9F%E5%8F%91%E5%A4%9A%E9%A1%B9%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/a-56296981 |dead-url=no }}</ref>1月21日，拜登又簽署十項抗疫行政令，涉及搭飞机及公交车时必须配戴口罩等內容。<ref>{{cite news |title=拜登密集签署行政令，全力启动新政府抗疫工作 |url=https://cn.wsj.com/articles/%E6%8B%9C%E7%99%BB%E5%AF%86%E9%9B%86%E7%AD%BE%E7%BD%B2%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E4%BB%A4%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%A8%E5%8A%9B%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8%E6%96%B0%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C-11611282010 |accessdate=2021-01-22 |archive-date=2021-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122025625/https://cn.wsj.com/articles/%E6%8B%9C%E7%99%BB%E5%AF%86%E9%9B%86%E7%AD%BE%E7%BD%B2%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E4%BB%A4%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%A8%E5%8A%9B%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8%E6%96%B0%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C-11611282010 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=拜登将签署10项行政命令对抗新冠疫情 |url=https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD/20210121-%E6%8B%9C%E7%99%BB%E5%B0%86%E7%AD%BE%E7%BD%B210%E9%A1%B9%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E5%AF%B9%E6%8A%97%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85 |accessdate=2021-01-22 |archive-date=2021-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128223328/https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD/20210121-%E6%8B%9C%E7%99%BB%E5%B0%86%E7%AD%BE%E7%BD%B210%E9%A1%B9%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E5%AF%B9%E6%8A%97%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85 |dead-url=no }}</ref>1月25日，拜登签署一项行政命令，要求美國政府增加采购对美国製造的产品。<ref>{{cite news |title=拜登签署行政令“买美国货” 专家：以前就有，需采取更多措施 |url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/biden-buy-american-20210125/5751798.html |accessdate=2021-01-28 |archive-date=2021-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128203728/https://www.voachinese.com/a/biden-buy-american-20210125/5751798.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>1月27日，拜登簽署行政令，要求將应对气候危机置于美国外交政策和国家安全的中心位置，並鼓励发展[[清洁能源|清洁能源]]以轉變美国对[[化石能源|化石能源]]的严重依赖，暂停相關企業在美國联邦土地上开采石油和天然气。<ref>{{cite news |title=拜登：将应对气候危机置于美外交和国安政策中心 |url=http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2021/01-28/9398591.shtml |accessdate=2021-01-28 |archive-date=2021-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210201134712/http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2021/01-28/9398591.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>2月2日，拜登签署3项涉及纠正特朗普政府强硬移民政策的行政命令。<ref>{{cite news |title=拜登签署3项有关移民政策行政令，纠正特朗普政府强硬移民政策 |url=http://news.xhby.net/index/202102/t20210203_6969441.shtml |accessdate=2021-02-03 |archive-date=2021-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210203083532/http://news.xhby.net/index/202102/t20210203_6969441.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>拜登在上任内头两周所签署的行政命令比[[富兰克林·德拉诺·罗斯福|罗斯福]]以来的任何一位总统上任首个月内所签署的行政命令都多。<ref>{{Cite web|title=With 28 Executive Orders Signed, President Biden Is Off To A Record Start|url=https://www.npr.org/2021/02/03/963380189/with-28-executive-orders-signed-president-biden-is-off-to-a-record-start|accessdate=2021-03-23|work=NPR.org|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210214082819/https://www.npr.org/2021/02/03/963380189/with-28-executive-orders-signed-president-biden-is-off-to-a-record-start|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2月4日，拜登政府结束了美国对[[沙特领导的干预也门行动|沙特领导的干预也门行动]]的支持。拜登在首次以总统身份访问[[美国国务院|美国国务院]]时表示，“这场战争必须结束”，冲突造成了“人道主义和战略灾难”。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Biden ending US support for Saudi-led offensive in Yemen|url=https://apnews.com/article/biden-end-support-saudi-offenseive-yemen-b68f58493dbfc530b9fcfdb80a13098f|accessdate=2021-03-23|date=2021-02-04|work=AP NEWS|archive-date=2021-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204225629/https://apnews.com/article/biden-end-support-saudi-offenseive-yemen-b68f58493dbfc530b9fcfdb80a13098f|dead-url=no}}</ref>2月24日，拜登取消了前总统特朗普於2020年为应对[[2019冠狀病毒病疫情|2019冠狀病毒病疫情]]而实施的大多数移民限制措施，<ref>{{cite news |title=拜登撤销特朗普实施的大多数移民限制措施 |url=https://cn.wsj.com/articles/%E6%8B%9C%E7%99%BB%E6%92%A4%E9%94%80%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E5%AE%9E%E6%96%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%9A%E6%95%B0%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD-11614223210 |accessdate=2021-02-25 |archive-date=2021-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210615091640/https://cn.wsj.com/articles/%E6%8B%9C%E7%99%BB%E6%92%A4%E9%94%80%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E5%AE%9E%E6%96%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%9A%E6%95%B0%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD-11614223210 |dead-url=no }}</ref>不過拜登一系列寬鬆的移民政策導致美墨邊境的非法移民数量創20年来最高水平<ref>{{cite news |title=美墨边境出现20年来规模最大非法移民潮 |url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2021-03/17/c_1127220741.htm |accessdate=2021-04-29 |archive-date=2021-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210510175641/http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2021-03/17/c_1127220741.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2月25日，拜登政府“打击了[[叙利亚|叙利亚]]境内两个[[伊朗|伊朗]]所支持的民兵组织的据点，以回应过去两周对该地区美军的[[火箭弹|火箭弹]]袭击”。这也是美国军方在拜登领导下首次采取行动。<ref>{{Cite web|title=US carries out air strikes in Syria targeting Iranian backed militias|url=https://www.cnn.com/2021/02/25/politics/us-iraq-iran/index.html|accessdate=2021-03-23|last=CNN|first=Barbara Starr, Oren Liebermann and Nicole Gaouette|work=CNN|archive-date=2021-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210303104326/https://www.cnn.com/2021/02/25/politics/us-iraq-iran/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>
[[File:Joe_Biden_welcomes_Japanese_PM_Suga_to_the_White_House_April_2021_(2).jpg|thumb]]与[[日本首相|日本首相]][[菅义伟|菅义伟]]会面]] 
3月10日，美國國務院允许[[萨尔瓦多|萨尔瓦多]]、[[危地马拉|危地马拉]]和[[洪都拉斯|洪都拉斯]]三国合法在美居留移民的未成年子女赴美。<ref>{{Cite web|title=美国重启中美洲移民未成年子女与在美父母团聚计划-新华网|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2021-03/11/c_1127198877.htm|accessdate=2021-03-23|work=www.xinhuanet.com|archive-date=2021-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210510175701/http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2021-03/11/c_1127198877.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>3月11日，在[[世界卫生组织|世界卫生组织]]宣布[[COVID-19|COVID-19]]为全球大流行病一周年之际，拜登签署了《[[2021年美國救援方案法|2021年美國救援方案法]]》，一个由他提出并推动的1.9万亿美元[[经济刺激|经济刺激]]救济方案，旨在加快摆脱疫情影响并推动美国经济复苏。<ref>{{Cite web|title=H.R.1319 - 117th Congress (2021-2022): American Rescue Plan Act of 2021|url=https://www.congress.gov/bill/117th-congress/house-bill/1319|accessdate=2021-03-23|date=2021-03-11|last=Yarmuth|first=John A.|work=www.congress.gov|archive-date=2021-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210313014919/https://www.congress.gov/bill/117th-congress/house-bill/1319|dead-url=no}}</ref>该方案包括直接给大多数美国人支付救助金，延长增加失业救济金额的期限，为[[2019冠状病毒病疫苗|疫苗]]分发和学校重新开放提供资金，支持小企业和州及地方政府，扩大医疗保险补贴和儿童税收抵免。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Here's what's in Biden's $1.9 trillion economic rescue package|url=https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/14/politics/biden-economic-rescue-package-coronavirus-stimulus/index.html|accessdate=2021-03-23|last=CNN|first=Tami Luhby and Katie Lobosco|work=CNN|archive-date=2021-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210218023132/https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/14/politics/biden-economic-rescue-package-coronavirus-stimulus/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>拜登还尝试游说提高联邦最低工资标准，但在参议院议事法规专家表示该增加条款违反议事规定后未被纳入最终法案中。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Here are the highlights of Biden’s $1.9 trillion ‘American Rescue Plan.’|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/14/us/biden-american-rescue-plan.html|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2021-01-14|accessdate=2021-03-23|issn=0362-4331|language=en-US|first=Jim|last=Tankersley|first2=Michael|last2=Crowley|archive-date=2021-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210214151741/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/14/us/biden-american-rescue-plan.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=What’s in the Stimulus Bill? A Guide to Where the $1.9 Trillion Is Going|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/03/07/us/politics/whats-in-the-stimulus-bill.html|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2021-03-07|accessdate=2021-03-23|issn=0362-4331|language=en-US|first=Thomas|last=Kaplan|archive-date=2021-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210312200200/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/03/07/us/politics/whats-in-the-stimulus-bill.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

