whitehouse.gov/briefing-room/statements-releases/2021/06/24/statement-by-president-joe-biden-on-hong-kongs-apple-daily/ |access-date=2021-06-24 |archive-date=2021-06-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210625013119/https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefing-room/statements-releases/2021/06/24/statement-by-president-joe-biden-on-hong-kongs-apple-daily/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

